```plantuml
@startuml Luizbrandt_users-crud-salesforce
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Client

rectangle "MuleSoft API" {
  rectangle "API Kit Router" as Router #lightblue
  rectangle "Mule Flows" as Flows #lightblue
  rectangle "DataWeave" as DataWeave #lightblue
  rectangle "Error Handling" as ErrorHandling #lightblue
  rectangle "Secure Properties" as SecureProps #lightblue
}

rectangle "Salesforce Connector" as SFConnector #lightgreen

database "Salesforce\n(Custom_User__c)" as SalesforceDB #lightyellow

Client --> Router : HTTP Request
Router --> Flows : Route Request
Flows --> DataWeave : Transform Data
Flows --> ErrorHandling : Handle Errors
Flows --> SFConnector : Perform CRUD
SFConnector --> SalesforceDB : CRUD Operations
SecureProps --> SFConnector : Provide Credentials
@enduml
```